    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 p-4" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-cookie-bite me-2"></i>What Are Cookies?
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit our website. They help us provide you with a better experience by remembering your preferences and understanding how you use our site.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-list me-2"></i>Types of Cookies We Use
                        </h2>
                        
                        <div class="cookie-type-card mb-3 p-4 rounded" style="background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
                            <h3 class="h6 text-light mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Essential Cookies (Always Active)
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off. They enable core functionality such as security, network management, and accessibility.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="cookie-type-card mb-3 p-4 rounded" style="background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;">
                            <h3 class="h6 text-light mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-warning me-2"></i>Analytics Cookies
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting and reporting information anonymously. This helps us improve our site.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="cookie-type-card mb-3 p-4 rounded" style="background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;">
                            <h3 class="h6 text-light mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-sliders-h text-info me-2"></i>Preference Cookies
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                These cookies enable the website to remember choices you make (such as language preference) and provide enhanced, more personal features.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="cookie-type-card p-4 rounded" style="background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;">
                            <h3 class="h6 text-light mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-bullhorn text-secondary me-2"></i>Marketing Cookies (Not Currently Used)
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                                We do not currently use marketing or advertising cookies on our website.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-cog me-2"></i>Managing Your Cookies
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-muted lh-lg mb-3">
                            You can control and manage cookies in several ways:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Cookie Preferences:</strong> Use our cookie banner to accept or decline non-essential cookies</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> Most browsers allow you to refuse cookies or delete existing ones</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Third-Party Tools:</strong> Use opt-out tools provided by third-party analytics providers</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="alert alert-warning mt-3" style="background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                            <strong>Note:</strong> Blocking or deleting cookies may affect your experience and some features may not work properly.
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt me-2"></i>Third-Party Cookies
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            Our website may use third-party services that set cookies, including:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>EmailJS:</strong> For contact form functionality</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> For typography</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Font Awesome:</strong> For icons</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock me-2"></i>Cookie Duration
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            Cookies can be either:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Temporary cookies that expire when you close your browser</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain on your device for a set period or until you delete them</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-2"></i>Updates to This Policy
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
                            We may update this cookie policy to reflect changes in technology or legislation. Please check this page periodically for updates.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-muted small"><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2025</p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-question-circle me-2"></i>Questions?
                        </h2>
                        <p class=" text-muted lh-lg">
                            If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-3 p-3 rounded" style="background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);">
                            <p class="text-light mb-0"><strong>Email:</strong> b.klodtattoo@gmail.com</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-gold px-5 py-3 rounded-pill">
            <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Back to Home
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

